<h2>mltool</h2>
<h3>Machine Learning Toolkit</h3>
<p>Haskell Machine Learning Toolkit includes various methods of supervised learning: linear regression, logistic regression, SVN, neural networks, etc. as well as some methods of unsupervised methods: K-Means and PCA.</p>
